target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China Guide</FONT></A> -- News links devoted to 50th anniversary celebrations. <LI><A HREF="http://dailynews.muzi.net/event/PRC_50th_Birthday/index.shtml" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Muzi.net -- Daily news</FONT></A> -- China's 50th birthday news. </UL><A NAME="3"><H3>Social issues</H3></A><UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.freechina.net/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Free China Movement</FONT></A> -- Pro-democracy information, links and discussion pages. <LI><A HREF="http://www.igc.apc.org/hric/index.html" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Human Rights in China</FONT></A> -- Press releases and information about human rights in China. <LI><A HREF="http://www.interlog.com/~yuan/china.html" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Democracy Wall of China</FONT></A> -- Pro-democracy site with links, information and photo galleries. <LI><A HREF="http://www.freetibet.org/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Free Tibet</FONT></A> -- News, information, advice, links and events about Tibet. </UL><A NAME="4"><H3>Local news coverage</H3></A><UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.cnd.org/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China News Digest</FONT></A> -- Photo archives, libraries, reference and articles.<LI><A HREF="http://www.insidechina.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Inside China Today</FONT></A> -- News, archives, shopping and discussion. <LI><A HREF="http://asiadragons.com/china/news/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China News Stand</FONT></A> -- Stock market, business, culture, travel and personal pages. <LI><A HREF="http://www.chinanews.org/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China Internet Information Center</FONT></A> -- News, government white pages, press releases and entertainment. </UL><A NAME="5"><H3>Country guides</H3></A><UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.china-contact.com/e.html" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Contact China</FONT></A> -- Chat rooms and searches, plus news, business, government, travel, history, culture, festivals and provinces. <LI><A HREF="http://www.flashpaper.com/beijing/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Beijing Page</FONT></A> -- Extensive list of links on Beijing, including photos, museums, tourism and entertainment. <LI><A HREF="http://china-window.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China Window </FONT></A>-- Links to several Chinese province sites. <LI><A HREF="http://www.chinatoday.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Chinatoday.com</FONT></A> -- Catalog of links including news, military, diplomacy, education and international trade. </UL><A NAME="6"><H3>Tourism guides</H3></A><UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.chinats.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China Travel System</FONT></A> -- Province and city guide that links to 30 places in China. <LI><A HREF="http://www.tibet-tour.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Tibet Tourism Bureau</FONT></A> -- Travel information, weather, transportation and sightseeing. <LI><A HREF="http://macau.tourism.gov.mo/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Macau Tourism Home Page</FONT></A> -- General information, sightseeing, food, hotels and special events.<LI><A HREF="http://www.china-sd.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Shandong on the Internet</FONT></A> -- Economy, business and information. <LI><A HREF="http://www.shanghai-ed.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Shanghai-ed -- Shanghai's home on the Web</FONT></A> -- Nightlife, business, real estate, hotels and travel. <LI><A HREF="http://www.magicoftibet.com/home.html" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">The Magic of Tibet</FONT></A> -- Culture and politics. </UL><A NAME="7"><H3>Search engines</H3></A><UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.muzi.net/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Go Muzi</FONT></A> -- Comprehensive search engine for news, photos, information and entertainment. <LI><A HREF="http://www.chinavista.com/home.html" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China Vista</FONT></A> -- Searchable yellow pages, business news, exhibitions and travel. <LI><A HREF="http://gochina.miningco.com/mbody.htm?PID=2745&amp;COB=home" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China for Visitors</FONT></A> -- Search engine for news, city information, visitor guides and chat forums. <LI><A HREF="http://www.surfchina.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Surf China</FONT></A> -- China-related search catalog. <LI><A HREF="http://www.itlinks.com/china/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Asia Links</FONT></A> -- Search engine for Asian related links. </UL><A NAME="8"><H3>Cultural resources</H3></A><UL><LI><A HREF="http://acc6.its.brooklyn.cuny.edu/~phalsall/images.html#Maps" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Brooklyn College Chinese Cultural Studies</FONT></A> -- Dozens of maps, archaeology resources, art and customs. <LI><A HREF="http://pasture.ecn.purdue.edu/~agenhtml/agenmc/china/china.html" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Art of China Home Page</FONT></A> -- Art, music, language, scenery and Chinese zodiacs.<LI><A HREF="http://www.china-guide.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China Guide Company</FONT></A> -- Alternative medicine, health food, cosmetics, arts, crafts, language instruction. <LI><A HREF="http://www.chinaexhibit.org/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China: Exploring the Interior</FONT></A> -- A collection of photographs of rural Chinese people during the Boxer Rebellion. <LI><A HREF="http://www.chinese-art.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Chinese-art.com Magazine</FONT></A> -- Articles, analysis, photo galleries and information on contemporary Chinese art. <LI><A HREF="http://www.redgategallery.com/index.htm" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Red Gate Gallery</FONT></A> -- Web gallery featuring contemporary Chinese art.<LI><A HREF="http://sunyatsen.hawaii.org/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Sun Yat-sen:  His Hawaii Roots</FONT></A> -- Sun Yat-sen Foundation of Hawaii homepage includes photos, sound, research and current events.</UL><A NAME="9"><H3>Businesses</H3></A><UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.chinesebusinessworld.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Chinese Business World</FONT></A> -- Business news and travel information. <LI><A HREF="http://www.chinapages.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">China Pages</FONT></A> -- Comprehensive listing of professional business sites. <LI><A HREF="http://www.ibc-global.com/asia/china/english.htm" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Internet Business Centers</FONT></A> -- Listing of Internet business centers in China. </UL><A NAME="10"><H3>Historical</H3></A><UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.gwu.edu/~nsarchiv/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">National Security Archive at The George Washington University</FONT></A> -- Contains documents of the Nixon-Chou meetings from 1972 as well as other National Security Archive documents. </UL><A NAME="11"><H3>Photo contributors</H3></A><UL><li><a href="http://www.aperture.org/" target="new"><font color="#0033FF">Aperture: Publisher of fine photographs</font></a></li><LI><A HREF="http://www.sjwar.org/Vm_site.htm" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Alliance for Preserving the Truth of Sino-Japanese War</FONT></A> <LI><A HREF="http://gochina.miningco.com/library/weekly/aa052899.htm?pid=2732&amp;cob=home" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Guizhou slide show by Shelley Wu</FONT></A> <LI><A HREF="http://www.si.edu/asia/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Arthur M. Sackler Gallery, Freer Gallery of Art</FONT></A> <LI><A HREF="http://www.albany.edu/museum/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">University Art Museum, Albany, New York</FONT></A> <LI><A HREF="http://www.ndmoa.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">North Dakota Museum of Art</FONT></A> <LI><A HREF="http://www.armenian-genocide.org/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Armenian National Institute</FONT></A> <LI><A HREF="http://www.brook.edu/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">The Brookings Institution</FONT></A> <LI><A HREF="http://www.remote.org/frederik/culture/berlin/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">Frederik Ramm: Fall of the Berlin Wall</FONT></A> <LI><A HREF="http://www.the-hurds.com/" target=new><FONT COLOR="#0033FF">David and Beth Hurd's Home Page</FONT></A></UL></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE><!--========================================================--><!--===============Paste story between here=================--><!--========================================================--></TD></TR></TABLE><BR clear=all><TABLE BORDER="0" WIDTH="600" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0"><TR><TD WIDTH=125  VALIGN=TOP><font face="Verdana, HELVETICA, ARIAL, sans-serif" size="1"><B><a href="#top"> Back to the top</a></B></font></TD><TD WIDTH="15">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="460" VALIGN=TOP><font face="Verdana, HELVETICA, ARIAL, sans-serif" size="1"><B>&#169; 2001 Cable News Network.</B> All Rights Reserved.<br><a href="/interactive_legal.html">Terms</a> under which this service is provided to you.<br>Read our <A HREF="/privacy.html">privacy guidelines</A>.</font><br></TD></TR></TABLE></BODY></HTML> contentType 9 text/html url 54 http://www.cnn.com:80/SPECIALS/1999/china.50/relateds/ responseCode 3 200 